e using it.  After that, you should be able to find what you need by looking at the tables of contents and browsing through the rest of the material.  If you have trouble, don't hesitate to ask an expert for help.e12jk40This handbook was originally prepared by Butler Lampson, and the present edition is the responsibility of Ed Taft.e12jk40